TrusteeCardSettings.walletPay.descriptio: Add your card to your Apple Pay wallet to get all the goodies of contactless payment
Add your card to your Google Pay wallet to get all the goodies of contactless payment
Open or download the Apple Wallet app
Click on the "+" button, and then on the item "Debit or credit card"
Click "Enter card details manually" and fill in the required fields. Then click "Save"
In the "First Name" field, you must enter your first and last name
Select SMS activation and wait for the activation code to arrive in the Trustee Plus app as a push notification. Make sure Trustee Plus push notifications are enabled
If there is only the item "Call by phone" - contact our support
TrusteeCardSettings.walletPay.android.st: Open or download the Wallet application
Click on the button "Add to wallet", and then click on the item "Payment card"
Click "Enter card details manually" and fill in the required fields. Then click "Save"
In the "Name" field, you must enter your first and last name in Latin
Confirm the details and press "Get SMS" and wait for the activation code to come to the Trustee Plus app as a push notification. Make sure that the push notifications for Trustee Plus are enabled
If the item "SMS" is missing - contact our support
